 MBOMBELA – His body was discovered in his Mercedes-Benz on Thursday morning. He had apparently driven off an embankment on the KaMagugu Road (R2256). The road is currently closed for the recovery. Police, traffic officers and the fire brigade are on the scene. Vally was reported missing on Tuesday. He was last seen at around 10:00 at Valencia Park. ALSO READ: Man found guilty for smuggling illicit goods A large search party had been looking for him ever since. Albert Gryvenstein from Bossies Community Justice helped to coordinate the effort. * This is a developing story and Lowvelder will update it as soon as more information becomes available. ALSO SEE: Ten-hour power cut planned for Mbombela